  "body": "[**![](https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/8fd2f0f5-1266-429b-b91c-d015a2026f31.webp)**](https://blocklegend001.dev/bh)\n\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://discord.gg/jVmUTGFMX5\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1051116089133777016?color=green&amp;label=Discord&amp;logo=Discord&amp;logoColor=green&amp;style=for-the-badge\" width=\"285\" height=\"40\"></a></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>This mod add 2 new items to the game: Tiny Coal &amp; Tiny Charcoal<br></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Break a piece of coal or charcoal into eight smaller pieces capable of smelting one item each.<br></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_587f74ac-3a79-4518-8aa8-6b80b66ae76b.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"481\" height=\"233\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_014209ba-3071-412d-9b91-d1c54042787e.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"477\" height=\"229\"></span></p>",
